00:03:59.780 --> 00:04:02.260
He's out in Seattle now
working with you guys.

00:04:02.260 --> 00:04:05.570
And he said he misses a
lot of things about Boston.

00:04:05.570 --> 00:04:08.434
He didn't mentioned
you, Steve, but he

00:04:08.434 --> 00:04:10.850
said he misses a lot of things
about Cambridge and Boston.

00:04:10.850 --> 00:04:13.690
And one of the main things
is his participation

00:04:13.690 --> 00:04:15.145
in citizen schools.

00:04:15.145 --> 00:04:16.720
But I want to thank Steven.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:21.160
And Steven needs to go to have
a conversation with the head

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:23.770
of the state network of
superintendents as part

00:04:23.770 --> 00:04:25.270
of the work he's
doing in education.

00:04:25.270 --> 00:04:28.689
So appreciate you being
here to do the introduction.

00:04:28.689 --> 00:04:30.480
Coming a little bit
later is another person

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:32.580
I want to think
just in absentia,

00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:35.670
and that's Steven Rothstein,
who is as of two days

00:04:35.670 --> 00:04:39.050
